# Generate PNG favicons from SVG
# You can run this if you have ImageMagick installed
# convert assets/favicon.svg -resize 32x32 assets/favicon-32x32.png
# convert assets/favicon.svg -resize 16x16 assets/favicon-16x16.png

# Or use online converters:
# 1. Go to favicon.io/favicon-converter
# 2. Upload your favicon.svg
# 3. Download the generated files
# 4. Add favicon-32x32.png and favicon-16x16.png to assets/ folder
